msgctxt "92_Himeka"
msgid "Tanimura-san!"
msgstr "¡Tanimura-san!"

msgctxt "104_Tanimura"
msgid "This is a surprise, is everything okay?"
msgstr "¿Qué ha pasado para que me llames de repente?"

msgctxt "116_Himeka"
msgid "That Kashiwabara guy was just at the club. He got really drunk and tore the place apart."
msgstr "Hace un rato, ese cliente Kashiwabara vino a al club, se emborrachó, armó un escándalo y luego se fue..."

msgctxt "128_Tanimura"
msgid "Did he hurt you?"
msgstr "¿Te lastimó?"

msgctxt "140_Himeka"
msgid "No... But I was scared. Maybe I should quit this job after all."
msgstr "No... Pero, me dio mucho miedo... No sé si debería seguir en este trabajo..."

msgctxt "152_Tanimura"
msgid "You should take the rest of the day off."
msgstr "¿Por qué no te tomas el resto del día libre?"

msgctxt "164_Himeka"
msgid "Yeah. Think I'll do that."
msgstr "Sí, tienes razón. Creo que lo haré."

msgctxt "176_Himeka"
msgid "Just talkin' to you makes me feel better."
msgstr "Con solo charlar contigo me siento mucho mejor."

msgctxt "188_Tanimura"
msgid "I'm here whenever you need me."
msgstr "Siempre estaré aquí para ti."

msgctxt "200_Himeka"
msgid "Thanks! Bye-bye."
msgstr "¡Gracias! ¡Hasta luego!"

msgctxt "260_Tanimura"
msgid "(Kashiwabara was wearing a black jacket if I remember correctly.)"
msgstr "(Kashiwabara llevaba una chaqueta negra, si no recuerdo mal)."

msgctxt "272_Tanimura"
msgid "(He might still be drunk and wandering around near the club.)"
msgstr "(Puede que todavía esté borracho y deambulando cerca del club)."

